      "id": "865379493161867",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "This is the definition of peak",
      "review_description": "This is hands down the best gorilla horror fan game of all time. From the moment you start playing, it pulls you in with its creepy atmosphere and intense jump scares. The dark maps, eerie sound effects, and unexpected moments keep your heart racing the entire time. What makes it so fun is how unpredictable it is — you never know when something is about to happen, which makes every round exciting. The controls feel smooth, and playing with friends makes it even better because everyone is screaming and laughing at the same time. It’s scary, competitive, and hilarious all at once. If you like horror games that keep you on edge and give you a real adrenaline rush, you should definitely download it.",
